{"about_the_game":"\u2018Crazy Farm: VR GROUND\u2019 is the party VR game which can be playing VR players and Mobile players together. Many VR games are played on solo with only one HMD devices, however 'Crazy Farm' can be played and enjoy via smart devices those are using by friends, family and lovers also. it contains three games that Mobile and VR can play together.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>'Non - VR Mode' UpDate! - Even if you have not any VR devices, you can enjoy the game!</i></strong></li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/extras/EP1_GIF.jpg?t=1542954307\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/extras/EP2_GIF.jpg?t=1542954307\" /><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/extras/EP3_GIF.jpg?t=1542954307\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Protect the farm</h2>In 'Protect the farm' mode, VR user hits an animal using a broom, a mobile user presses a button for a log time to take away an apple and eat it.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/extras/EP1_IMG.png?t=1542954307\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Protect the truck</h2>In 'Protect the truck' mode, VR user should throw apple bombs to prevent animals from reaching the truck. mobile user needs to hit a move button repeatedly to avoid an apology bomb and acquire an apple in the truck.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/extras/EP2_IMG.png?t=1542954307\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Protect the barn</h2>In 'Protect the barn' mode, it is necessary for the VR user to hit the animal flying to the barn using two brooms. mobile users need to fly in a safe direction to avoid farmers' broom and get apple.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/extras/EP3_IMG.png?t=1542954307\" /><br><br>Up to 11 players (1 HMD user, 10 mobile users) can play at the same time, and even if all 11 players are not equipped, you can enjoy the game with AI.<br>Play through 'Crazy Farm' to enjoy together with friends, family and lovers!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Future</h2>- Tutorials updates for smart device players.<br>- Web player that is can play without installing mobile application(PC can be connected also).","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1542954307","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1542954307","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1542954307","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/876130/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1542954307","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen PvP","id":37},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Cross-Platform Multiplayer","id":27},{"description":"Tracked Controller Support","id":52},{"description":"VR Only","id":54},{"description":"Remote Play Together","id":44},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"\u2018Crazy Farm: VR GROUND\u2019 is the party VR game which can be playing VR players and Mobile players together. Many VR games are played on solo with only one HMD devices, however 'Crazy Farm' can be played and enjoy via smart devices those are using by friends, family and lovers also. it contains three games that Mobile and VR can play together.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong><i>'Non - VR Mod